item.title: CVE-2023-40215|2023-11-03T23:15:12.400Z -- demonisblack -- demon%20image%20annotation
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection') vulnerability in Demonisblack demon image annotation allows SQL Injection.This issue affects demon image annotation: from n/a through 5.1.
